        Changelog
        =========
        
        
        v0.2.0 (2014-02-07)
        ----------------------------------------
        
        - Support searching for podcasts and episodes.
        - Improve performance by removing feedparser.
        - Improve handling of iTunes tags.
        
        
        v0.1.0 (2014-02-01)
        ----------------------------------------
        
        - Initial release.
        
